ZH: 杂交是将两个不同种类的植物或动物进行交配的过程。
EN: Hybridization is the process of crossing two different types of plants or animals.

ZH: 杂交玉米是一种由不同品种交配而成的玉米。
EN: Hybrid corn is a type of corn that is produced by crossbreeding different varieties.

ZH: 这种植物是通过杂交育种研究所培育出来的。
EN: This plant was developed through hybrid breeding research.

ZH: 杂交使得植物能够兼具不同种类的特点。
EN: Hybridization allows plants to possess characteristics of different species.

ZH: 研究人员对杂交育种的效果进行了深入的分析。
EN: Researchers conducted in-depth analysis of the effects of hybrid breeding.

ZH: 杂交犬是由两种不同犬种交配而成的。
EN: A hybrid dog is a mix of two different dog breeds.

ZH: 我们正在进行一项关于杂交动物的研究。
EN: We are conducting research on hybrid animals.

ZH: 杂交大米在提高产量和抵抗力方面有很大潜力。
EN: Hybrid rice has great potential in increasing yield and resistance.

